div.div:
ORACLE
- calls out to POST /api/proposal with {
intent: user's intent,
transcript_hash: ipfs hash of the transcript
}
- API ingests the intent of the user + message history and completes a finalized proposal
- API pushes proposal to IPFS
- API returns the IPFS hash to the oracle
- Oracle proposes contract to the DAO automatically
